{
  "stem": "11611.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It had been occupied by the Germans before the war, March of '39.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was virtually no damage anywhere in the city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a very low level economy, but they were producing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were better off than most of Central Europe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But what was most refreshing about the place was it wasn't damaged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It just wasn't rubble like Vienna, or Budapest, or any other city you could mention.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I liked the Czechs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When you went to Prague, although it was a bilingual city, both German and Czech, the Czechs would not respond to anything spoken in German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Obviously, I didn't speak any Czech, so I was limited to English there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you couldn't ask a question in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By this time, I was reasonably fluent in German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'd been there, let's say, a year or so.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Today, you go to Prague, you can't ask a question in Russian, but they'll freely respond to German, since the Germans own the country.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I would say so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I dealt with a-- I dealt with a-- with a Czech banker whose name was [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], ?] little [NON-ENGLISH], who had been a minister in various Czech governments after the war, generally agrarian and right wing, but I think-- and I got to know him fairly well.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the chairman of the board of a bigger Czech chain called the [NON-ENGLISH] banks, and I did deal with him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We collected records there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did the same thing in Holland too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I spent three weeks in the basement of a Dutch bank collecting records.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I went to Belgium and talked to-- again, in Holland, I'm trying to remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
